import { Component } from '@angular/core'; @Component({ selector: 'app-sidebar', templateUrl: './sidebar.component.html', styleUrls: ['./sidebar.component.css'] }) export class SidebarComponent { function(){ let btn:any = document.querySelector("#btn"); let sidebar:any = document.querySelector(".sidebar"); let searchBtn = document.querySelector(".bx-search"); sidebar.classList.toggle("active"); if(btn.classList.contains("bx-menu")) { btn.classList.replace("bx-menu", "bx-menu-alt-right"); } else { btn.classList.replace("bx-menu-alt-right", "bx-menu"); } } }
